</li>
<li><strong><a href="/bad-dreams">Bad Dreams</a></strong> <em>by Thefriendlyvandal</em></li>
<li><strong><a href="/scp-3621">SCP-3621</a></strong> Best Intentions <em>by DrMagnus</em></li>
