<li><strong><a href="/dr-bright-is-no-longer-allowed-to-use-temporal-anomalies">Dr. Bright Is No Longer Allowed To Use Temporal Anomalies In Order To Travel Back in Time So He Can Kill Hitler</a></strong> <em>by Doctor Cimmerian</em></li>
<li><strong><a href="/with-a-target">They Couldn't Hit The Broad Side Of A Barn With A Target Painted On It</a></strong> <em>by Doctor Cimmerian</em></li>
</ul>
<p>Please add tales in order of posting, unless it's a sequel or prequel to an existing story, in which case it should be listed as:</p>
<ul>
<li>Tale
<ul>
<li>Sequel/Prequel</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
